Class SpongeEntity<T extends net.minecraft.entity.Entity,E extends Entity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dockbox.selene.nms.entities.NMSEntity<T>
      • org.dockbox.selene.sponge.entities.SpongeEntity<T,E>
  • Type Parameters:

    public abstract class SpongeEntity<T extends net.minecraft.entity.Entity,E extends Entity>
extends NMSEntity<T>
implements Entity, SpongeComposite
    Represents common functionality for all entities implemented in Sponge.
